'''Construct'''是Scirra公司製作的以[[HTML5|HTML5]]為基礎的[[2D電腦圖形|2D]]遊戲編輯器<ref name="Create games with Construct 2">{{cite web| url=http://www.scirra.com/construct2| title=Create games with Construct 2| publisher=Scirra| accessdate=2016-06-18| archive-date=2016-06-06| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160606115553/https://www.scirra.com/construct2| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://news.yahoo.com/london-startup-scirra-launches-html5-game-creator-no-150245718.html | title=London Startup Scirra Launches HTML5 Game Creator | publisher=Yahoo News | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121226120055/http://news.yahoo.com/london-startup-scirra-launches-html5-game-creator-no-150245718.html | archivedate=2012-12-26 | accessdate=2016-06-18 }}</ref>，主要針對無[[程式設計|程式設計]]基礎者<ref>{{cite web | url=http://active.tutsplus.com/articles/reviews/review-construct-2-a-drag-and-drop-html5-game-maker/ | title=Construct 2, a drag and drop game maker | publisher=ActiveTuts+ | accessdate=2016-06-18 | archive-date=2013-06-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130603051617/http://active.tutsplus.com/articles/reviews/review-construct-2-a-drag-and-drop-html5-game-maker/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>，只需在視覺化編輯器中進行[[拖放|拖放]]動作，即可完成一個遊戲。

== 特徵 ==

=== 事件系統與行為 ===
在Construct 2中，編輯遊戲的主要方法是透過「事件表」，作用與[[程式語言|程式語言]]相近。每個事件分類中都有許多事件，其中包含[[條件運算式|條件運算式]]或觸發動作。一旦滿足條件，就可以開始運行<ref>How Events Work. (n.d) retrieved 2/25/2014, from Scirra Web Site: https://www.scirra.com/manual/75/how-events-work {{Wayback|url=https://www.scirra.com/manual/75/how-events-work |date=20160328214844 }}</ref>。不必去學習如[[邏輯或|OR]]、[[及閘|AND]]以及[[作用域|作用域]]等複雜的邏輯<ref>Gullen, A (2012, April, 13). Guide to Construct 2's advanced event features. retrieved 2/25/2014, from Scirra Web Site: https://www.scirra.com/tutorials/292/guide-to-construct-2s-advanced-event-features {{Wayback|url=https://www.scirra.com/tutorials/292/guide-to-construct-2s-advanced-event-features |date=20160328104641 }}</ref><ref>Event Groups. (n.d) retrieved 2/25/2014, from Scirra Web Site: https://www.scirra.com/manual/80/groups {{Wayback|url=https://www.scirra.com/manual/80/groups |date=20160328064640 }}</ref>。人們可以透過啟用或停用事件，來製作一個事件組合。

